    • visit

      public boolean visit​(org.eclipse.jdt.core.dom.BreakStatement node)
      This method is an overwritten method from the super class ASTVisitor. This method visits all the BreakStatement ASTNodes within the CompilationUnit. BreakStatement ASTNodes follow the format of: BreakStatement: break [ Identifier ] ; This method determines key information of the Statement in the CompilationUnt. It then creates a new Statement object and sets these values within the class. Returns true to search for a child ASTNode.
